body.description: Simplify all of your electrical projects around the home with the Eastman dishwasher power cord kit. This dishwasher power cord kit is designed with a plug configuration of NEMA 5-15R and features a voltage power rating of 13 Amps or 125 Volts for indoor use. This dishwasher power kit measures 5.3 feet in length and is equipped with (1) 3-prong power cord with a built-in harness and (3) wire nuts. Made of heavy-duty 16-gauge wire, the Eastman dishwasher power cord kit fits most major brands of dishwashers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 9, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Temp rated wire with 3/8 clip
reviews.reviewText: I install appliances for a living so have gone through a good amount of these wires... the good? Its a high temp wire meaning it wont melt underneath your dishwasher. I've looked around and that isnt easy to find. Being pre-clipped with that adapter makes it very convenient as well. The bad? It used to be about $8... at the time of this writing this wire is being sold for $17, but you can find this wire at the home despot for $12. Also the adapter is for 3/8in knock outs and in most cases will wiggle around after you install it. You can buy the connector, the wire, and the wire nuts seperately and save a good amount of money or just go buy the kit at a big box store because in terms of value it just isnt worth it.

I bought a dishwasher online and didn't came with the plug. This plug is amazingly easy to assemble and not hard to hook up to the device . It is affordable and now I don't need to do the dishes everyday. Really happy thanks

reviews.reviewTitle: Easy to install, litterally plug and play
reviews.reviewText: Purchased for a new Samsung dishwasher. Surprised in the manual there is a whole section of required pieces and accessories that are not included in order to install. After some research found this complete kit with all of the necessary pieces. I did have to replace cable clip (not sure of the term) as gray one included was too small snap into place, was just worried about tension on the wire if I pulled my dishwasher out. That was mainly due to my model dishwasher. Could not find a similar kit in any of the local big box retailers and an electrician was going to cost $150 to hardwire it in.
It works very well! The price is good for the quality.
Got this for my new dishwasher. Installation is simple and straightforward. Excellent price compared to my local hardware stores. The only thing is the harness is too small for my Samsung dishwasher.
